FeatureH2MySQLInstallation❌ Not needed✅ Must installData saved permanently❌ No✅ YesSetup time⚡ 0 minutes🕐 10-15 minutesGood for learning✅ Perfect✅ YesGood for real apps❌ No✅ YesSee data in browser✅ h2-console✅ MySQL WorkbenchSpeed⚡ Very fast🚀 Fast

